    AirAsia Job Vacancies 2021 - Data Automation Programmer

    January 8, 2021

    TOC

    • Vacancy
    • How To Apply

    AirAsia job vacancies 2021 for Data Automation Programmer position which based in Kuala Lumpur. Jawatan kosong AirAsia 2021 terkini untuk kekosongan Data Automation Programmer penempatan di Kuala Lumpur.

    Vacancy

    • Data Automation Programmer

    Job Description

    Big Loyalty Engineering & Technology Team is a technology centre that designs and builds all-in-one travel and lifestyle products for people in ASEAN. The technology centre comprises a team of software engineering and technology experts based in Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia) and Bangalore (India).

    We believe in diversity, intellectual curiosity, analytical and openness. We are looking for someone to join our growing team in Kuala Lumpur to be part of the Digital and Cultural transformation @ Big Loyalty.

    Here’s what an ordinary day looks like:

    • You will develop and maintain the data pipeline components that require coding/scripting in GCP.

    • You will develop/code interfaces between data pipeline components to/from web services such as API.

    • You will monitor the status of the data pipeline execution and rectify or escalate issues if the execution fails.

    • Participate in team discussion for data solution designing

    You got to have these to carry out the job :

    • Proactive in seeking out new data related technologies that can help the business;

    • Able to work independently with minimal supervision;

    • Thinking out of the box;

    • Motivated to learn new technologies and applying them in work

    The job is ideal for you if you:

    • Have at least 5 years working experience

    • Experienced working with cloud platform (especially GCP) or any cloud databases

    • Experienced working with interfaces such as API and web services

    • Knowledge of technologies such as below:

      • Python programming;

      • JAVA programming;

      • PHP programming;

      • R programming (optional);

      • MS SQL Server;

      • MySQL;

      • Amazon RDS;

      • Google BigQuery;

      • Google Cloud SQL;

      • GCP Data Analytics products (such as Cloud Data Fusion, Cloud Composer, Pub/Sub, Dataflow, Google Data Studio…etc)

    What makes an Allstar employee? Y

    You allow yourself to ‘Dare to Dream’ big dreams and seize the day. You ‘Make things Happen’, you like taking efforts and achieving it. Without any effort, no dream will get fulfilled.

    Our companies include Airasia.com, BigPay, Teleport, RedBeat Ventures, AirAsia Foundation, Tune Group of Hotels, TuneProtect, OURSHOP, FORM.AT, Airasia Ads

    We are all different - one talent to another - that is how we rely on our differences. At AirAsia, you will be treated fairly and given all chances to be the best. We committed to creating a diverse work environment and are proud to be an equal opportunity employer. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, gender, gender identity or expression, sexual orientation, national origin, genetics, disability, age, or veteran status.
